FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776096667
OL,3,CPolice renew manhunt information
OL,4,Cappeal two years on from stabbing in
OL,5,CCroydon
OL,7,FPolice have already secured two
OL,8,Fconvictions for the murder.
OL,10,FDavid Walcott and Rammon Mali were
OL,11,Fjailed for life at the Old Bailey last
OL,12,FApril.
OL,14,FThe killing happened as stallholders
OL,15,Fat the fruit and vegetable market were
OL,16,Fpacking up for the day, and cleaners
OL,17,Fwere moving in, shortly before 6pm.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776096667
OL,3,CPolice renew manhunt information
OL,4,Cappeal two years on from stabbing in
OL,5,CCroydon
OL,7,FAfterwards, the defendants and a third
OL,8,Fsuspect headed to The Spread Eagle pub
OL,9,Fand bought three pints of Guinness
OL,10,Fwith a #20 note.
OL,12,FJordan Vincent believed to be from
OL,13,FSouth London, remains at large and is
OL,14,Fwanted by police in connection with
OL,15,Fthe case.
OL,17,FScotland Yard appealed for any
OL,18,Finformation that could reveal his
OL,19,Fwhereabouts or lead to his arrest and
OL,20,Fconviction.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
